mailbox_sent   get "mailbox/trash" =&gt; "mailbox#trash", as: :mailbox_trash     resources :conversations do     member do       post :reply       post :trash       post :untrash     end   end end </code></pre>  <p>So if anyone can help how to get out of this. Thanks in advance.</p>